{"tid":41872,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"剷除一切高登舊思想、習慣、文化、風俗","createTime":"2016-12-16T08:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T09:04:52.000Z","uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0d1fa52a4e8ab7063f40b73e797ee5f390e93e","tid":41872,"uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"連登成立左咁耐，好多用語、潮文，陳規陋習，仍然散發高登林早洩既腐朽氣息。<br />\n連登唔應該做高登2.0 ，如果唔係d人就會慢慢回流高登。<br />\n<br />\n我地由宜家呢個moment作出最後通牒，向舊世界宣戰，要一齊將呢d代表着舊高登林氏階級階級思想既潮語同風俗習慣，黎個大掃除。<br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\n少用高登用語，咩巴打絲打，想用就死返高登啦。<br />\n唔比提自己係幾幾年會員，係連登大家都係16年會員。"},{"pid":"635d84d5e3d671a7c027f26e246de12cab222734","tid":41872,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593d048b45bcfc40b699f183db951f146be2c54c","tid":41872,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"唔同意 巴絲打呢個稱呼係屬於巴絲打本身<br />\n係屬於「人」而唔係屬於「地方」<br />\n你咁做等同班唔識中文既人 乜都當係蝗語送哂比中共一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6bac7f2189880e5c7b85e8055c702bf90bbe4d","tid":41872,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"yes<br />\n仲用高登野真係好肉酸"},{"pid":"671a09b8ff434c634a80faef16833130f9d90e9a","tid":41872,"uid":45019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:36:33.000Z","msg":"文革"},{"pid":"e235dc7cb56a8bada8d2b3a872e42c29de39823b","tid":41872,"uid":55575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:37:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>yes<br />\n仲用高登野真係好肉酸</blockquote><br />\n同意(唔好講agger)😂😂😂"},{"pid":"df58527d8a28b4383e42e423a6a57b6a779728f9","tid":41872,"uid":58666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T08:40:44.000Z","msg":"批鬥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab47fab43bedbb1e6d99eaa7534d